{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2106270, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "感觉够呛？", "timestamp": 1626834576, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106272, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你要在航空公司停止检录之前到柜台检录就行了", "timestamp": 1626834598, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106275, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一般这个截止时间会提前一个小时", "timestamp": 1626834612, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106277, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": 2106270, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 那正常应该提前多久啊？我坐高铁什么都喜欢踩点到，不喜欢在候车厅等。", "timestamp": 1626834620, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106278, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "第一次你还这么冒险。。", "timestamp": 1626834645, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106279, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": 2106275, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我靠，提前这么多", "timestamp": 1626834651, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106286, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": 2106278, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 这些APP都让我提前一个半小时或者两小时到，我感觉很不可思议啊", "timestamp": 1626834696, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106287, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": 2106279, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 一般坐飞机都要早一点。。", "timestamp": 1626834701, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106292, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一般都比起飞时间至少提前两小时吧…", "timestamp": 1626834745, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106296, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "建议查一下最晚值机时间，如果没有需要托运的也不是不能踩点", "timestamp": 1626834766, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106300, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有些公司会45分钟前停止值机，如果不能自助值机或者有托运的建议早点去", "timestamp": 1626834837, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106303, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 对对那个叫最晚值机时间，dave专业", "timestamp": 1626834852, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106314, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": 2106277, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 因为飞机安检手续啥的比高铁繁琐，踩点去很可能凉凉", "timestamp": 1626834965, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106323, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": 2106296, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 没有要托运的，我按开始登机时间提前半小时，这个应该没啥问题了吧", "timestamp": 1626835039, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106327, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "当然来不及了，提前45分钟～一小时就停止check-in了", "timestamp": 1626835087, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106336, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "一般起飞前四十五分钟就不能值机了，建议一般提前一个半小时到，而且你第一次去大兴机场，一开始容易迷路，大兴机场比其他机场更大更绕。", "timestamp": 1626835141, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106341, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": 2106323, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 你看看app上能不能自助值机，简而言之就是因为乘飞机你要拿票的，光有身份证不行的，拿票还要安排座位", "timestamp": 1626835191, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106346, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": 2106323, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 如果dz是接下来马上要来不及了的话", "timestamp": 1626835206, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106348, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": 2106341, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 值机就是约等于拿票加托管行李的意思", "timestamp": 1626835235, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106360, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": 2106348, "tag": null, "text": "明白了，谢谢各位dy，幸亏在这多问了一句", "timestamp": 1626835337, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106363, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": 2106323, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 只要确认能值机就没啥大问题（这里默认为登机时间非起飞时间）", "timestamp": 1626835362, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106373, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "第一次还是早两个小时到更合适", "timestamp": 1626835535, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106382, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "来不及", "timestamp": 1626835648, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2106487, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 409346, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果有网上值机，没托运行李，用电子登机牌的话，起飞之前半小时到绰绰有余。\n假设起飞前15分钟停止登机\n你到了机场后，只需要走向“国内出发”里没有人排队的VIP安检（保安看你登机时间会带你去的），然后3分钟过安检，最多5分钟小跑到登机口，近的话快走也够了，这样你还剩7分钟，非常富余\n我也是喜欢踩点的，基本不会提前一个小时以上到，等太久了烦\n如果dz和我一样从小就喜欢掐着秒踩点，掐秒经验丰富的话，提前半小时到绰绰有余了\n如果需要现场值机，那你得提前45分钟以上到值机柜台，这还得视柜台排队的人多不多，一般提前50分钟也足够了。", "timestamp": 1626837273, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 409346, "reply": 24, "tag": null, "text": "dz第一次坐飞机，请问提前半小时到大兴机场能来得及吗？", "timestamp": 1626834545, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1626837272, "url": "", "vote": {}}}